dismissalText.commentary: Rachin Ravindra c Duckett b Carse 18 (25b 4x4 0x6 38m) SR: 72

dismissalComment.html: steered tamely to gully! There's a long, anxious wait while they check for the no-ball - but no reprieve for Ravindra! Carse looked like he was about to be sick, having bowled Williamson while overstepping last week. But Rod Tucker is eventually satisfied there was some boot behind the line and Ravindra, who had paused his walk from the field, has to go. Not a threatening ball but played loosely in the air, and Duckett holds on to this chance. England strike moments before the break
